NetPacket/SpanningTree version 0.01
===================================

This is the NetPacket::SpanningTree Module.  it works in concert with the NetPacket::Ethernet and NetPacket::LLC module to decode Spanning Tree and Rapid Spanning Tree data.  It will also encode RST and ST data.  Please refer to the perldoc for more information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  NetPacket::Ethernet
  NetPacket::LLC

